  Also a contribution goes towards my other doors (such as KewlPage), you will
  also recieve regular news and information if you have E-Mail access! Read
  the file @{b}-Why-Register??-@{ub} for more information!

@{u}Finally...@{uu}
  
   I would be very grateful if you register !!, you will also recieve developer
information, like file structures and also a bunch of other configs, screens
and things :o).

